headline: Ameren Missouri plans new project as part of low-cost, balanced energy mix to serve customers
summary: Today, Ameren Missouri, a subsidiary of Ameren Corporation (NYSE: AEE), announced plans to develop an additional low-cost energy source to power 44,000 homes and provide 300 construction jobs.
